      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garaged, and there isn\u2019t a single scratch or dent to be found. It runs like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. You won\u2019t find another one this clean at this price! Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
