    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in immaculate condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline via independent throttle bodies. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, short-throw engagement, paired with a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis is exceptional, with no subframe fatigue and a suspension geometry that remains tight and communicative. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the interior exhibits no bolster wear or pixel degradation. Recent comprehensive maintenance includes a full VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement, ensuring this high-strung powerplant is turn-key ready for the purist collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
